<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Eligibility</title>
    <link href="eligibility/eligbilite.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script language="javascript">

        function clear_offer() {
            document.getElementById('contract_id').value = "";
			document.getElementById('name').value = "";
			document.getElementById('firstname').value = "";
			document.getElementById('serial_number').value = "";
			document.getElementById('equipment_type').value = "";
			document.getElementById('offer_type').value = "";
			document.getElementById('eligibility').innerText = "";
		
        }
        function search_offer() {
            if (document.getElementById('contract_id').value != "") {
                //document.getElementById('name').value = "Kopp";
                //document.getElementById('firstname').value = "Julien";
                document.getElementById('serial_number').value = "8966-447LM";
                document.getElementById('equipment_type').value = "985-145";
                document.getElementById('offer_type').value = "Promo Noël";
                document.getElementById('eligibility').innerText = "Yes";
            }
        }
	</script>
